data.meta_description: Zoe Salmon: Zoe Salmon. Actress: Get Him to the Greek. Zoe Salmon was born on 7 January 1980 in Bangor, County Down, Northern Ireland, UK. She is an actress, known for Get Him to the Greek (2010), Face Value (2010) and Hot Rods (2008). She has been married to William Corrie since 2016.
